<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Card Layout with Images</title>

    <style>
        body{
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        .card-container{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .card{
            background-color: white;
            width: 260px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card img{
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-content{
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .card h2{
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .card p{
            font-size: 14px;
            color: gray;
        }

        .card button{
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border: none;
            background-color:blue;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card button:hover{
            background-color:blue;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="card-container">

        <div class="card">
            <img src="nature.jpg.png">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Nature</h2>
                <p>Nature is the beautiful and essential force that sustains life on Earth. 
                    It encompasses everything around us, from the towering trees and vast oceans to the smallest insects and flowers.  </p>
                <button>Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="Mountains.jpg.png">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Mountains</h2>
                <p>Mountains are significant natural elevations of the Earth's surface, 
                    rising steeply above their surroundings to create unique ecosystems, weather patterns, and biodiversity.</p>
                <button>Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="beaches.jpg.png">
            <div class="card-content">
                <h2>Beach</h2>
                <p>Beaches are dynamic coastal landforms composed of loose particles like sand,
                     gravel, or shell fragments, formed by wave action and erosion over thousands of years.</p>
                <button>Read More</button>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>